{"tid":2187320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[3/9 腦殘人數統計] 逾88萬人預約　47萬人完成採樣","createTime":"2020-09-03T14:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T14:28:31.000Z","uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4704c21021388e3c8d96a1eb68707ec6600b492b","tid":2187320,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"政府表示，由今日（3日）早上8時至晚上8時，共有約19.2萬名市民，於全港各社區檢測中心登記檢測，而計劃在9月1日開展以來，累計合共有約47萬名市民在檢測中心登記檢測。自8月29日網上預約開始以來，截至今日晚上8時，累計有約88.4萬名市民成功預約檢測。<br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n預約人數已經放緩<br />\n尋日79.8萬名市民成功預約檢測<br />\n今日有約88.4萬名市民成功預約檢測<br />\n一日增加不足十萬<br />\n<br />\n採樣腦殘數目方面<br />\n第一日12.6萬<br />\n第二日15.2萬<br />\n第三日19.2萬<br />\n<br />\n依走勢有機會有百幾萬，接近二百萬腦殘去拮鼻<br />\n大家唔好掉以輕心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bfaabcefbb7f6ce7063790d18b8c98179f4533","tid":2187320,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39a181db6291098c89100fd79f6c916d65f1de1","tid":2187320,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><